{
  "text": "Clonal lines of asexual S. mediterranea were used for all experiments and were maintained at 20\u00b0C in 1.0x Montju\u00efc salts [CITATION_1] . Animals were fed weekly with organic calf liver paste. To minimize non-specific gut background from feeding, animals were starved for at least 1 wk prior to fixation for in situ hybridization and immunohistochemistry.",
